meta {
  name: Batch Members
  seq: 1
}

auth {
  mode: inherit
}

docs {
  # Batch Members

  Manages student membership in batches.

  ## Endpoints
  - POST   /api/v1/batch-members              — Add a student to a batch
  - GET    /api/v1/batches/:id/members         — List all members of a batch
  - DELETE /api/v1/batch-members/:batchID/:userID — Remove a student from a batch

  ## Allowed Status Values
  - Active
  - Graduated
  - Suspended
  - Withdrawn

  ## Variable Flow
  Add Batch Member → saves {{BATCH_MEMBER_USER_ID}}
  Remove Batch Member uses {{BATCH_ID}} + {{BATCH_MEMBER_USER_ID}}
}
